    "description": "<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Devouring Dark Form]</p>\n<p>You gain a tentacle unarmed attack with 10-foot reach that deals 1d8 bludgeoning damage and has the grapple trait.</p><hr /><p><strong>Heightened (2nd)</strong> You can choose to take on the shark battle form from <em>animal form</em> instead of gaining a tentacle unarmed attack.</p>\n<p><strong>Heightened (5th)</strong> You can choose to take on the water elemental battle form from <em>elemental form</em> instead of gaining a tentacle unarmed attack.</p>",
